---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Astro Blog">
	<main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto p-8">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">üßë‚ÄçüöÄ Hello, Astronaut!</h1>
		<p class="mb-4">
			Welcome to the official <a
				href="https://astro.build/"
				class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Astro</a
			> blog starter template. This template serves as a lightweight, minimally-styled
			starting point for anyone looking to build a personal website, blog, or
			portfolio with Astro.
		</p>
		<p class="mb-4">
			This template comes with a few integrations already configured in
			your
			<code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">astro.config.mjs</code> file. You
			can customize your setup with
			<a
				href="https://astro.build/integrations"
				class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Astro Integrations</a
			> to add tools like Tailwind, React, or Vue to your project.
		</p>
		<p class="mb-2">
			Here are a few ideas on how to get started with the template:
		</p>
		<ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-1">
			<li>
				Edit this page in <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded"
					>src/pages/index.astro</code>
			</li>
			<li>
				Edit the site header items in <code
					class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded"
					>src/components/Header.astro</code>
			</li>
			<li>
				Add your name to the footer in <code
					class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded"
					>src/components/Footer.astro</code>
			</li>
			<li>
				Check out the included blog posts in <code
					class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded">src/content/blog/</code>
			</li>
			<li>
				Customize the blog post page layout in <code
					class="bg-gray-100 px-1 rounded"
					>src/layouts/BlogPost.astro</code>
			</li>
		</ul>
		<p class="mb-4">
			Have fun! If you get stuck, remember to
			<a
				href="https://docs.astro.build/"
				class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">read the docs</a
			>
			or <a
				href="https://astro.build/chat"
				class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">join us on Discord</a
			> to ask questions.
		</p>
		<p>
			Looking for a blog template with a bit more personality? Check out
			<a
				href="https://github.com/Charca/astro-blog-template"
				class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">astro-blog-template</a
			>
			by <a
				href="https://twitter.com/Charca"
				class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">Maxi Ferreira</a
			>.
		</p>
	</main>
</Layout>
